  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[使用pandas处理数据]]></title>
    <link href="http://libre.me/blog/2014/04/17/pandas-read-csv/"/>
    <updated>2014-04-17T08:20:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://libre.me/blog/2014/04/17/pandas-read-csv</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Python 现在越来越多地被用于处理数据与科学计算，其中比较有名的有Numpy和Scipy。但是随着技术的发展，越来越多的优秀的扩展被开发出来，像IPython，Pandas，Seaborn等等。</p>

<p>使用Pandas包可以非常轻松地对数据进行导入与清洗。以下使用Ipython QT处理数据：</p>

<p>数据导入函数: <strong>read_csv()</strong></p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='python'><span class='line'><span class="o">%</span><span class="n">pylab</span> <span class="n">inline</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">pandas</span> <span class="kn">as</span> <span class="nn">pd</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">read_csv</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/88478120/datasets/iris.csv&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">header</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">print</span> <span class="n">data</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>如图所示：</p>

<p><img src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/88478120/blog/20140402/read_csv.png" alt="read_csv" /></p>

<p>获取一列数据：</p>

<pre><code>col = data["sepal length"]
print col
</code></pre>

<!-- more -->


<p>或者：</p>

<pre><code>col = data[[2]]
print col
</code></pre>

<p>获取多列数据：</p>

<pre><code>cols = data[["sepal length", "sepal width"]]
print cols
</code></pre>

<p>或者：</p>

<pre><code>cols = data[[2,4]]
print cols
</code></pre>

<p>获取一行</p>

<pre><code>row = data[3:4]
print row
</code></pre>

<p>获取多行数据：</p>

<pre><code>rows = data[3:9]
print rows
</code></pre>

<p>组合：</p>

<p>取出单个数据：</p>

<pre><code>a = data[2:3]
b = a[[3]]
print b
</code></pre>

<p>取出矩形数据</p>

<pre><code>a = data[[1,3,4]]
b = a[4:8]
print b
</code></pre>

<p><strong>时间序列处理</strong>
导入数据：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='python'><span class='line'><span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">read_csv</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/88478120/datasets/D0301.csv&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">header</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">index_col</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">print</span> <span class="n">data</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>如图所示：</p>

<p><img src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/88478120/blog/20140402/read_csv2.png" alt="read_csv2" /></p>

<p>此时时间索引列为字符串格式，需要将其转换成时间格式</p>

<pre><code>print data.index
data.index = pd.to_datetime(data.index)
print data.index
</code></pre>

<p>获取统计信息：</p>

<pre><code>data.head()
data.tail()
data.describe()
data.count()
data.mean()
data.sum()
data.std()
data.max()
data.min()
</code></pre>

<p>简单绘图：</p>

<pre><code>col = data[[0]]
col.plot()
</code></pre>

<p>图形如下所示：</p>

<p><img src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/88478120/blog/20140402/timeserise.png" alt="plot" /></p>
]]></content>
