    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Python Tkinter 布局管理]]></title>
    <link href="http://libre.me/blog/2014/04/13/tkinter-layout/"/>
    <updated>2014-04-13T20:20:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://libre.me/blog/2014/04/13/tkinter-layout</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在Tkinter中有三种方式可以对组件进行布局管理，它们分别是pack,grid,place。</p>

<p><strong>pack:</strong>
由简单的组件组成的应用程序可以用pack布局，而且通过设置参数可以实现随窗口缩放的组件。通常与frame搭配也可以实现复杂的布局管理，但是没有grid清晰与简洁。</p>

<p><strong>grid：</strong>
对于由许多个组件组成的复杂的程序用grid布局，效率比较高。但是无法实现组件随窗口而缩放。</p>

<p><strong>place：</strong>
place用于对组件进行精确的布局，place由像素制定位置，应用不多。</p>

<h2>pack</h2>

<p>pack使用比较简单，基本在组件名称后加上pack()函数就实现打包。</p>

<p><strong>语法：</strong></p>

<pre><code>widget.pack( pack_options )
</code></pre>

<p><strong>参数：</strong></p>

<ol>
<li>expand   随窗体的缩放而缩放</li>
<li>fill</li>
<li>side     (TOP,BOTTOM,RIGHT,LEFT)</li>
</ol>


<p><strong>实例：</strong></p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>tkinter.py</span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
<span class='line-number'>17</span>
<span class='line-number'>18</span>
<span class='line-number'>19</span>
<span class='line-number'>20</span>
<span class='line-number'>21</span>
<span class='line-number'>22</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='python'><span class='line'><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">Tkinter</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="o">*</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">root</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Tk</span><span class="p">()</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">frame</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Frame</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">root</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">frame</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pack</span><span class="p">()</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">bottomframe</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Frame</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">root</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">bottomframe</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pack</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">side</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">BOTTOM</span> <span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">redbutton</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Button</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">frame</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">text</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&quot;Red&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">fg</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&quot;red&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">redbutton</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pack</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">side</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">LEFT</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">greenbutton</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Button</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">frame</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">text</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&quot;Brown&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">fg</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&quot;brown&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">greenbutton</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pack</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">side</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">LEFT</span> <span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">bluebutton</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Button</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">frame</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">text</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&quot;Blue&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">fg</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&quot;blue&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">bluebutton</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pack</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">side</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">LEFT</span> <span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">blackbutton</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Button</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bottomframe</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">text</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&quot;Black&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">fg</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&quot;black&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">blackbutton</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pack</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">side</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">BOTTOM</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">root</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">mainloop</span><span class="p">()</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>



]]></content>
